About Silverleaf Resorts



 


 





Welcome to Silverleaf Resorts
We built our company, Silverleaf Resorts, Inc., around four distinguishing factors: value, variety, convenience and flexibility. Our commitment to implementing those key factors in everything we do is what made us a leader in the vacation ownership industry.




Ozark Mountain Resort, Missouri - Silverleaf Resorts

  

  









 Message from the CEO



Alt Text: 

Tom Nelson Silverleaf Resorts



Title Text: 




​Tom Nelson - President, Silverleaf Resorts 
Welcome,Everyone deserves the opportunity to create fun and memorable vacation experiences. These are the precious moments you share with families and loved ones that you never forget.We can make that dream come true for you—with the flexibility and convenience to enjoy it on your own terms. Silverleaf Resorts offers a variety of vacation experiences in unique destinations. Plus, with the many resort amenities and activities provided, there’s something for everyone to enjoy.You are at the heart of everything we do. Our entire team is committed to providing you the finest product, highest levels of service and genuine enthusiasm to make every vacation special. Let us help you create more of life’s best moments. Tom NelsonPresidentSilverleaf Resorts
  

 








About Silverleaf



Silverleaf Resorts is a company structured around four defining qualities: Value, variety, convenience and flexibility. Our goal is to provide you a fun and memorable vacation experience with every visit. We do this by placing a strong emphasis on each of these qualities. And through our commitment to bring a network of great resorts with country club-style amenities within reach of families just like you.
But it doesn’t stop there. Our resorts feature a diverse selection of on-site programs, activities and amenities. This helps further ensure that your family vacation is everything it should be. With our premiere resort properties strategically located in Texas and Missouri, there’s a perfect vacation property waiting for you.




Career opportunites at Silverleaf
At Silverleaf Resorts, we are always looking for people with enthusiasm and integrity to join our team. We approach our work with energy and look for people who thrive on pushing themselves to do their best every day.
See available positions
 




History

Alt Text: 





Title Text: 





 









1985



1990



1995



2000



2005



2010



2015






1989
Silverleaf Resorts opens with seven resorts in Texas & Missouri


 


1997
Silverleaf Resorts becomes a publicly traded company
Timber Creek Resort opens, serving the St. Louis market
Fox River Resort opens, serving the Chicago market


 


1998
Oak n' Spruce Resort opens,
serving the New England / 
New York market


 


1999
Apple Mountain Resort opens in the Blue Ridge Mountains, serving the Atlanta Market


 


2000
Silverleaf’s Seaside Resort 
opens a beach recreation area 
in Galveston, TX


 


2004
Orlando Breeze Resort opens in family theme-park destination of Orlando, FL


 


2011
Silverleaf Resorts was acquired in May 2011 by Cerberus Capital Management, L.P. and as a result became a private company


 


2014
Silverleaf Resorts, Inc. Announces the Grand Opening of Pirate’s Cay Indoor Water Park at Fox River Resort.


 


2015
Silverleaf is acquired by Orange Lake Holdings, home to the Holiday Inn Club Vacations® brand.
Fox River, Oak n’ Spruce and Apple Mountain properties rebranded to Holiday Inn Club Vacations resorts.


 


2016
Holiday Hills, Piney Shores, Orlando Breeze, Hill Country, Villages, Galveston Seaside and Timber Creek properties rebranded to Holiday Inn Club Vacations resorts.


 




 










